CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 14, 1961, pg. A30, reads: "Bulwarks of the 'House' - These three senior linemen are typical of the young giants who keep football rivals of Westinghouse High School on the losing side, as Coach Dimperio's Bulldogs roar toward the 1961 City League crown.  Left to right: Larry Maloney, Charles Harris and Bobby Henderson.  The trio played solid individual roles last week, as Taylor Allderdice fell, 42-7. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Westinghouse High School football players Larry Maloney, Charles "Charlie" Harris, and Bobby Henderson, posed on Westinghouse field
